data.text: @gregobr @MobileSyrup I had the same issue today, and also with Ragnarok on the day it went live. Might be a timed issue, just takes a little while to have the search and feeds update when it goes live? I dunno 🤷‍♂️

@MobileSyrup Is it weird that it was hard to find? I had to search the entire title before it came up. Meanwhile Ragnarok and all sorts of other popular titles are right there when you log in... Odd...
